Implementation summary:
- Added a real-time Supabase subscription in `components/admin/restock/restock-requests-list.tsx` that listens for `INSERT` events on `public.restock_requests`.
- On each new restock submission, the UI now:
  - Shows an in-app toast notification.
  - Triggers a browser push notification using the Web Notifications API.
  - Refreshes the restock order list immediately so monitoring is live.
- Added `lib/client-notifications.ts` helper to standardize browser notification behavior and permission handling.
