How to verify:
- Open `/admin/restock` in two sessions (e.g., admin and pharmacist).
- In one session, submit a new restock order via `/admin/restock/new`.
- Confirm in the other session (without manual refresh):
  - A toast appears saying a new restock order was submitted.
  - A browser notification appears (if permission is granted).
  - The new order appears in the list in real-time.

